    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Heat</strong> a wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid which you'll use later) with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> vegetable oil over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> hot, add the pancetta and cook for 5 min or until just beginning to crisp</p>",
