        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, combine the mayonnaise, red wine vinegar, dill and 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> milk with a pinch of salt and pepper</p>\r\n<p><strong>Stir</strong> to combine - this is your dressing</p>\r\n<p><strong>Taste</strong> for seasoning, adding more pepper if needed&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
