    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Once</strong> the pancetta is cooked, stir in the breadcrumbs and a small knob of butter</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tip:</strong> scrape up the bits of pancetta that are stuck to the pan (they're the best bits!)</p>",
